the taking. Use it!

15
00:02:22,666 --> 00:02:24,125
[YAMOTO]
This is my power now.

16
00:02:24,208 --> 00:02:26,625
[SHI NINJA]
Yes! Use it to the fullest.

17
00:02:26,708 --> 00:02:29,666
