of rage coming from?

29
00:03:14,625 --> 00:03:16,833
What matters now,
is that they are mine.

30
00:03:16,916 --> 00:03:19,458
I feel this rage.

31
00:03:19,541 --> 00:03:21,916
You saved my life.

32
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,000
[sobbing]

33
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:31,291
