34
00:03:31,375 --> 00:03:32,791
[continues sobbing]

35
00:03:32,875 --> 00:03:35,833
[YAMOTO] But they didn't.
It's gonna be okay.

36
00:03:35,916 --> 00:03:38,000
Let's go home.

37
00:03:41,875 --> 00:03:43,875
[car horns honking]

38
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,875
[ASARI] Hey, Yamoto-san.
It's so good to see you.

39
00:03:47,958 --> 00:03:49,875
