70
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,291
[GANG BOSS, MEMBERS]
Abbah!

71
00:05:27,375 --> 00:05:28,750
Heh.

72
00:05:31,083 --> 00:05:36,833
[distant sirens wail]

73
00:05:36,916 --> 00:05:38,166
Back off, man.

74
00:05:38,250 --> 00:05:40,375
