already lettin' me out?

76
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,000
Mm?

77
00:05:49,083 --> 00:05:52,125
Well, Domo, Shogo-san.
I am Fumatoni.

78
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:54,916
