88
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,458
[GUARD 03A]
Abba-ba-ba-ba-bah!

89
00:06:21,541 --> 00:06:23,958
Ugh. You're like
a rabid animal.

90
00:06:24,041 --> 00:06:26,375
--[FUMATONI] Yeeart!
--[SHOGO] Aaaargh!

91
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:28,666
