100
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:49,916
It would seem you find
yourself at a crossroads.

101
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:53,583
Join our syndicate and live,
or refuse and die.

102
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:55,875
What is your decision?

103
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:07,958
[PUNK NINJA]
Domo, Shogo-san.

104
00:07:08,041 --> 00:07:10,416
You know death
will be the end, right?

105
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,916
[SHOGO]
Who are you?

106
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,000
[PUNK NINJA]
Right, I'm Punk Ninja.

107
00:07:14,083 --> 00:07:15,875
