121
00:08:16,708 --> 00:08:18,541
[JOCK 03A] No we're done!
And we're very sorry!

122
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:20,666
But please, don't tell
anybody about this!

123
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,416
