but only if you promise

124
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,833
to never try it again.

125
00:08:23,916 --> 00:08:25,875
[JOCKS]
Yes! We promise!

126
00:08:29,375 --> 00:08:31,416
[YAMOTO]
That boy is just like me.

127
00:08:32,875 --> 00:08:36,500
[YAMOTO] We're exactly
the same. Our fates.

128
00:08:42,958 --> 00:08:45,916
[ASARI] Yamoto-san!
Are you okay?

129
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,250
