worry about. Everything's fine.

132
00:08:53,291 --> 00:08:54,458
[ASARI sighs]

133
00:08:54,541 --> 00:08:56,541
[YAMOTO] You should be
more worried for them.

134
00:08:56,625 --> 00:08:59,041
--[ASARI sobbing]
--[YAMOTO] Don't cry.

135
00:08:59,125 --> 00:09:01,375
[YAMOTO] Why were they talking
about me in the first place?

136
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:03,041
Well, uh. The word got out

137
