was revived by a ninja soul.

181
00:11:09,041 --> 00:11:10,666
What amazing providence!

182
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,750
You both escape death,
become possessed,

183
00:11:12,833 --> 00:11:14,958
and transfer to
the same high school.

184
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:17,583
